2) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new loss function for facilitating competitive learning. 
3) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning discriminative image representations for a specific task. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with large-scale image retrieval and localization. 
5) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with retrieving geo-tagged reference images from a large database.
